sequenceDiagram
    actor Teacher
    participant UI as Dashboard
    participant API as Web API
    participant DS as DataStore
    participant Repo as RepositoryService
    participant Plag as PlagiarismService
    participant AI as AiReviewService
    participant Final as FinalizationService

    Teacher->>UI: Login and choose task
    UI->>API: GET classes/tasks/submissions
    API->>DS: Load state
    API-->>UI: List of submissions

    Teacher->>UI: Pull repositories
    UI->>API: POST /pull-repos
    API->>Repo: Pull(...)
    Repo-->>API: sync results
    API-->>UI: rows ok/error

    Teacher->>UI: Run plagiarism
    UI->>API: POST /review/plagiarism
    API->>DS: SubmissionById
    API->>Plag: Analyze
    Plag-->>API: plagiarismScore
    API-->>UI: score

    Teacher->>UI: Run AI check
    UI->>API: POST /review/ai
    API->>DS: SubmissionById
    API->>AI: Analyze
    AI-->>API: aiScore + decision
    API-->>UI: score + report

    Teacher->>UI: Finalize and send
    UI->>API: POST /review/finalize
    API->>Final: Approve
    UI->>API: POST /review/send-email
    API->>Final: Send
    Final-->>API: sent/fallback
    API-->>UI: done